| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1193 — Recovery Inhibition (knight)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aa9dd7c2-4fa1-5a16-890b-8a1440e5b4d7"
